1
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:27,959
My lord Left Chancellor

2
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:29,400
I trailed them the whole way

3
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:31,120
To the forest edge of Zhenyuan County

4
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,120
They split into two groups

5
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:33,439
Golden Guard Pan took the main road

6
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,439
The other three slipped into the forest

7
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,480
I laid an ambush in the woods

8
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,799
And shot Ning Chen dead

9
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,359
Where is the body?

10
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:42,079
The...

11
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,560
The body...

12
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:50,519
I did indeed shoot Ning Chen dead

13
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:52,439
He plunged from a sheer cliff into the river

14
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,319
There is no way he survived

15
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:54,680
I...

16
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,879
"No way he survived"?

17
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:01,560
Is this how I taught you to do things?

18
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,760
I want to see the man if he's alive,

19
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,480
and his corpse if he's dead.

20
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,080
Now go, find him at once!

21
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:09,639
Yes, my lord

22
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:16,879
Forgive me, my lord Left Chancellor

23
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:31,520
Young master, you're awake.

24
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:34,080
You were in the water for a long time.

25
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:36,199
My daughter Lian'er carried you back.

26
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,560
Your fever wouldn't break.

27
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,759
You've been unconscious.

28
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:40,199
Lian'er.

29
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,439
Bring some water.

30
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,159
Have some water first.

31
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,439
I'll do it myself.

32
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:51,599
Don't drink too much.

33
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:54,159
You've been out for a day and a night.

34
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:55,319
I'll go brew some medicine for you.

35
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:56,520
You rest for a while.

36
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,039
Much obliged.

37
00:02:59,159 --> 00:02:59,879
Old Man Li.

38
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:05,319
You owe the Imperial Uncle four months' rent.

39
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:08,159
Debts must be repaid. That's only natural.

40
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,159
If you can't produce the money today,

41
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:13,240
we'll take your daughter as payment.

42
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,039
Steward Zhang, please.

43
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,479
Please show some mercy.

44
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,319
Just a few more days.

45
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:20,319
I'll definitely pay the rent.

46
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:21,719
I beg you, I beg you.

47
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:23,280
Spare my daughter.

48
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,599
The Imperial Uncle has taken a liking to her.

49
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:28,960
You should be delighted.

50
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,360
The Imperial Uncle has said,

51
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,800
once your daughter is his,

52
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:35,759
all your debts will be wiped clean.

53
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,159
No, please...

54
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:39,000
Men, take this girl away!

55
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,759
Don't keep the Imperial Uncle waiting.

56
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:42,400
Guards!

57
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,120
You can't! You can't!

58
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,159
You can't!

59
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,840
You blind old fool!

60
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,719
How dare you defy the Imperial Uncle!

61
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,719
You old wretch!

62
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:51,840
Father!

63
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:52,400
Father!

64
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:54,479
Who is it?

65
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,080
Who dares strike me?

66
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,759
The Imperial Inspectorate.

67
00:04:01,439 --> 00:04:02,319
Good, you recognize it.

68
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:06,479
Don't believe me?

69
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:07,919
Here, take the badge.

70
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:09,960
Verify it yourself.

71
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,719
Greetings, my lord.

72
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:16,959
Damn it.

73
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,439
How did someone from the Imperial Inspectorate

74
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,759
suddenly turn up here?

75
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,319
In broad daylight,

76
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,839
attempting to abduct a commoner's daughter.

77
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,040
Who gave you such gall?

78
00:04:26,639 --> 00:04:27,319
My lord.

79
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:30,040
I serve the Imperial Uncle.

80
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:33,920
He is the elder brother of the current Empress.

81
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:35,480
You dare strike me?

82
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:37,759
That's defying the Imperial Uncle himself.

83
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,680
The Empress's brother...

84
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,560
Could the corruption in Zhenyuan County

85
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:43,680
and the suffering of the people

86
00:04:44,279 --> 00:04:45,439
be tied to the Imperial Uncle?

87
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,720
Now you know to be afraid?

88
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:51,879
As they say, imperial power doesn't reach the countryside.

89
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,399
In this Zhenyuan County,

90
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,160
the Imperial Uncle is heaven itself.

91
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,240
Heaven, my ass!

92
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,959
Forget a lowly thug like you.

93
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,360
Even if the Imperial Uncle himself came today,

94
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,360
I'd still beat him all the same.

95
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,079
My lord, spare me! My lord!

96
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:10,519
Stop, stop hitting him!

97
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,199
Any more and you'll kill him!

98
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,160
If he dies here,

99
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,439
the Imperial Uncle may not touch you,

100
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:17,959
but he'll never spare

101
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,560
the two of us, father and daughter.

102
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,439
For the sake of these two today,

103
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,319
I'll spare your worthless life.

104
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,519
Take me to the Imperial Uncle at once.

105
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,879
I'd like to see

106
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:32,319
who in this dynasty

107
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,399
truly is heaven.

108
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,079
My lord.

109
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,199
My lord.

110
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:42,639
I have something important to tell you.

111
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,720
Old man, what are you doing?

112
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:45,000
Get up at once.

113
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:45,600
No, no, no.

114
00:05:46,279 --> 00:05:46,759
My lord.

115
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,680
Though my eyes grow dim,

116
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:51,319
my judgment of character remains sharp.

117
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,240
My lord.

118
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,680
You are full of righteous fervor,

119
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,879
upright and kind.

120
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:56,600
For the people of Zhenyuan County,

121
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:59,720
I have a most important item

122
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,800
to entrust to you.

123
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,360
What is this?

124
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,079
My lord

125
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,240
There is something you might not know.

126
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:13,000
The former clerk of Zhenyuan County

127
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:15,000
was my dear friend for many years

128
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:16,480
He still had a conscience.

129
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,959
He gathered evidence of corruption

130
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:20,040
from the prefect down to the magistrates

131
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,240
across all of Chongzhou,

132
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,680
and recorded it in this very ledger.

133
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:28,439
Zhenyuan County is no longer a place fit for men

134
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:30,879
The Imperial Uncle, the Empress's brother,

135
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,959
has made this place his treasure trove.

136
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,360
Elder Li speaks the truth

137
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:38,319
Zhenyuan County has long become a living hell

138
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:40,360
The Imperial Uncle, drunk on royal favor

139
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:42,120
preys upon the common folk

140
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,959
Hu Qiang and his ilk abuse their power

141
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:45,800
committing every manner of evil

142
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:48,199
The officials collude as one

143
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,920
Their tyranny is fiercer than tigers

144
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:53,120
The people have no clothes to cover themselves

145
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,160
and no food to fill their bellies.

146
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,920
Tree bark and grass roots are their daily fare

147
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,040
Such misery

148
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,920
is beyond anything ever heard of

149
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:04,079
Aren't these men from the Imperial Uncle's manor?

150
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:05,600
How were they beaten so badly?

151
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,519
And, and bound up like this?

152
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:12,879
This man doesn't dress like an ordinary official.

153
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:15,319
Could he have come to save us?

154
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,120
Really?

155
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,279
Imperial Uncle

156
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,519
Please

157
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,120
Golden Guard Pan

158
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,160
Come

159
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,839
Let us share another cup, you and I

160
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,519
Thank you, Imperial Uncle

161
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,920
Come, gentlemen

162
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:47,639
Please

163
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,839
Golden Guard Pan

164
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,519
Our town is a poor and remote backwater.

165
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:55,439
Such a small place

166
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:58,079
We have nothing worthy to offer you

167
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,519
Forgive our poor hospitality

168
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:01,040
I beg your pardon

169
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,920
Lord Ai, you are too kind

170
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,240
Imperial Uncle

171
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,519
You worthless wretch!

172
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,279
How many times have I told you?

173
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:22,120
Only maidens of marriageable age

174
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:24,000
These rotten, ugly creatures

175
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:25,759
have no business prancing about here!

176
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:28,040
Imperial Uncle

177
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,040
Calm your wrath

178
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:29,959
Please, calm down

179
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,240
If your ears serve no purpose

180
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:39,759
I shall rip them off and feed them to the dogs

181
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:40,960
Do you hear me?

182
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:43,399
I will bear it in mind.

183
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,720
Get out, get out!

184
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:45,840
Yes, my lord

185
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:54,759
Golden Guard Pan.

186
00:08:55,879 --> 00:08:56,879
If you fancy her,

187
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,720
she is yours.

188
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:01,799
Thank you, Imperial Uncle.

189
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,480
Allow me to pour your wine.

190
00:09:03,639 --> 00:09:04,039
Good.

191
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:04,799
Come, come, come.

192
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:05,759
Let us raise a toast.

193
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:06,840
To these distinguished lords from the capital.

194
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,320
My lords, let us drink together.

195
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:10,360
I thought the Imperial Inspectorate's

196
00:09:10,519 --> 00:09:12,000
Golden Guards were truly incorruptible.

197
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:13,600
Who would have thought

198
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:15,320
they accept both money and women.

199
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,879
Drink your fill.

200
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,720
Once you've had your fun, get lost.

201
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,000
No one shall disturb

202
00:09:20,159 --> 00:09:22,320
my reign as the king of Zhenyuan County.

203
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,639
Let me feed you, my lord.

204
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,879
I can manage. I can manage.

205
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,639
Come now, my lord.

206
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,240
That won't do.

207
00:09:33,879 --> 00:09:34,600
Ning Chen.

208
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,000
What is he doing here?

209
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:43,840
Who goes there?

210
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,320
Such audacity!

211
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:47,240
To barge into the Imperial Uncle's estate!

212
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,559
Ning Chen, you...

213
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,960
Golden Guard Pan.

214
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:53,240
Is this man your subordinate?

215
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:56,879
Ning Chen.

216
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,639
The Imperial Uncle is here. Mind your manners.

217
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,200
What do you think you are doing?

218
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,600
Well, isn't this grand.

219
00:10:04,799 --> 00:10:06,679
Outside, the people are in rags

220
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,440
and starving.

221
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:11,360
Yet here you are, building high stages

222
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,679
and indulging in boundless extravagance.

223
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:17,759
You're nothing but beasts in human skin.

224
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:19,840
Ning Chen!

225
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,480
My good lord,

226
00:10:26,679 --> 00:10:27,720
do calm yourself.

227
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:30,279
What on earth has made you so furious?

228
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:31,440
Who are you?

229
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:33,360
I am

230
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:37,279
the magistrate of Zhenyuan County,

231
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:40,320
Ai Wenguang.

232
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,159
You...

233
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,879
Even as a man of the Imperial Inspectorate,

234
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:48,000
you can't just beat an imperial official as you please.

235
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:50,120
So you know you're an imperial official?

236
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,799
As the magistrate of Zhenyuan County,

237
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,639
while your people starve to death,

238
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:57,559
you indulge in luxury here.

239
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,120
You beast, worse than swine!

240
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,000
Ning Chen!

241
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:01,879
Stop this!

242
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,840
I am the Imperial Uncle,

243
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:07,799
elder brother of the reigning Empress.

244
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:09,320
This is my estate.

245
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,159
In broad daylight,

246
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,039
you dare commit violence here?

247
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,600
Such audacity!

248
00:11:14,799 --> 00:11:15,679
Shut your mouth!

249
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,200
As the Imperial Uncle,

250
00:11:17,559 --> 00:11:19,200
you ought to uphold the laws of Daxuan,

251
00:11:19,759 --> 00:11:21,200
preserve the dignity of the royal house,

252
00:11:21,679 --> 00:11:22,799
and cherish the people as your own children.

253
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:24,919
But what have you done, you corrupt dog?

254
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:26,960
You...

255
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:31,120
You let these thugs seize women by force,

256
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:32,360
treating human life like dirt.

257
00:11:32,519 --> 00:11:34,960
You haven't done a single decent thing!

258
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,559
So, Imperial Uncle,

259
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,480
do you acknowledge your crimes?

260
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,720
This is outrageous!

261
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:43,919
Even His Majesty has never rebuked me so.

262
00:11:44,399 --> 00:11:45,720
You, a mere Silver Guard,

263
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,480
dare to spew such impudent words?

264
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:54,279
Even if what you say is true, so what?

265
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,639
Here in Zhenyuan County,

266
00:11:57,679 --> 00:12:00,159
do you dare lay a hand on the Imperial Uncle?

